","requires_auto_position":false},"notes[0].title":"📁 Folder Configuration","notes[1].content":"## Workflow Flow\n\n1. **Define Folders** - Configure the nested folder structure to deploy\n2. **List Companies** - Fetch all companies from Hudu\n3. **Filter Active** - Remove archived companies (and filter by target company if specified)\n4. **Check Existing** - Get existing folders for each company (with-items)\n5. **Flatten & Determine** - Flatten nested hierarchy with depth levels, exclude existing folders\n6. **Initialize** - Set current_depth=0, max_depth, and known folders list\n7. **Create at Depth** - Create all folders at current depth level (with-items)\n8. **Update & Check** - Add newly created folders to known list, increment depth\n9. **Loop** - If more depth levels exist, go back to step 7\n\n### Workflow Input\n| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |\n|-----------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `target_company_name` | String | No | If provided, only targets this specific Hudu company. Leave empty to target all active companies. |\n\n### Features:\n- ✅ Skips archived companies\n- ✅ Skips folders that already exist (idempotent)\n- ✅ **Supports unlimited nesting depth**\n- ✅ Processes folders level-by-level (parents before children)\n- ✅ Concurrent API calls (5 at a time per level)\n- ✅ Easy to add new folders via nested JSON structure\n- ✅ Optional single-company targeting","notes[1].metadata":{"x":-63.31000000000006,"y":108.71999999999991,"fill":"rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.08)","width":458,"height":356,"stroke":"rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.7)","padding":20,"task_ids":["019c96a178ea77f6b8d9ef6ee36d4922","019c96a194467d54bca5a565f1b91a2b","019c96a1b77f7dff8905de42792ddbc6","019c96a1d68278afb729398a1a1bb2a1","019c96ae6bbc76ffa1f7f59deb0e8d87","019c96a201107cc99dc20ddf95d805fc","019cb994402d7ebdbd6bc02340ddeae5"],"fillEnabled":true,"positioning_mode":"task_container","requires_auto_position":false},"notes[1].title":"🔄 Workflow Overview","parameters.target_company